## Writing rules

- Lead with the sharpest useful insight.
- Use source links for source-derived claims.
- Keep paragraphs short.
- Use active voice. Prefer subject-verb-object.
- Use contractions where natural.
- Never fabricate statistics, customer results, or operational claims.
